{"id":203772,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/维权网-查建国：关于重判“西南二陈”的声明/","date":"2011-12-30T05:24:57Z","modified":"2015-12-05T05:47:23Z","title":"维权网 | 查建国：关于重判“西南二陈”的声明","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"> </a>授权维权网发布</p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>惊悉两小时前，在这年终“收关”之际，川黔两省当局捍然判民主人士“西南二陈”以重刑。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>贵阳中级法院以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">36</span><span>篇文章中摘录文字为证据，以“煽动颠覆国家政权”为罪名，判贵州人权研讨会负责人陈西</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>年徒刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>四川地方法院以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>篇文章中摘录文字为证据，判四川民主异议人士陈卫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>年徒刑。）这是中国民主人士前仆后继，又一次付出牺牲的一页。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>我抗议</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>但不悲伤，因为这是我们必然要付出的牺牲！在这风雨如晦的长夜，不断加强对民主人士镇压，这能阻止民主转型的历史步伐吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>默默地去坐牢，放下身外之物名与利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>默默地去坐牢，用自己的这个“行为艺术”对中国民主转型做出微薄贡献。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>默默地去坐牢，坚守心中的“良知”，在自己固守的精神家园中遨游。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>让暴风雨来得更猛烈些吧！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>我时刻准备着，打点行装再坐牢。为了我可爱的祖国自由的明天，我愿以自己老弱之躯乃至生命，把牢底坐穿！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>壮哉，向“西南二陈”致敬！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>向王炳章、刘晓波、刘贤斌、高智晟、郭泉等大批在监狱默默坚守的战友致敬！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>北京　查建国</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-221693437516043796?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n<p>Loading&#8230;</p>\n","author":1001,"categories":[1],"tags":[9041,15158]}